data.description: An absolutely exquisite post & beam cabin with Craftsman-style flair. Two hand-built wood-burning fireplaces and a wood stove. Newly updated kitchen. No maintenance LVP floors. Enjoy three seasons room off Great Room and drink in the beauty of the wood lands. Outside the home has a mix medium of chink board and mortar, vinyl shakes, river stone and metal lap roof. Huge deck, two-car garage, large storage unit. All with USFS border. Also county water and a well. Enjoy the amenities of community green space including trout stream, beach and fishing pond.
